what it can do for you.

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:47.890
It can ease your
emotional pain.

00:38:47.890 --> 00:38:50.600
It can restore your cognitive
functioning.

00:38:50.600 --> 00:38:52.640
It can help you think
more clearly.

00:38:52.640 --> 00:38:55.130
It can minimize risks of
infection, like we saw with

00:38:55.130 --> 00:38:59.050
