long-term mental health.

00:38:59.050 --> 00:39:01.780
It can minimize risks to
your physical health.

00:39:01.780 --> 00:39:04.120
And it can increase
your emotional

00:39:04.120 --> 00:39:05.590
resilience over time.

00:39:05.590 --> 00:39:08.350
These self-esteem exercises,
for example, will increase

00:39:08.350 --> 00:39:11.980
your emotional resilience,
if you do them regularly.

00:39:11.980 --> 00:39:15.870
So look, I hope I've been able
to convince you to invite

