something that needs as much

00:39:22.420 --> 00:39:26.450
attention and as much care as,
yes, you give your teeth.

00:39:26.450 --> 00:39:27.280
And I've looked at you all.

00:39:27.280 --> 00:39:28.390
You all have good teeth.

